  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the mysterious world of Ancient Egypt! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find matching tiles, solve mahjong levels and collect artifacts to uncover secrets of Giza valley, Old city, Desert and Nile.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/f3c6ff7a5d81ba425bd1421bb71743bf.avif?t=1730482880\" width=642 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Restore artifacts collection!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover how the Great Pyramid of Giza was constructed, how Egyptians learned to read hieroglyphs, why Only the pharaoh could own a cat in Ancient Egypt and many more surprising facts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/14d17df1595897670fbc1e5b31474690.poster.avif?t=1730482880\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/14d17df1595897670fbc1e5b31474690.webm?t=1730482880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We made it even better with new game features. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you will find huge treasures, tricky locks, new bonus tiles and more. Solving some layouts is not easy, but you can always use powerups to beat the most challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/f40d1433067430f126b8a298988c5257.avif?t=1730482880\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras_big/f40d1433067430f126b8a298988c5257.avif?t=1730482880 width=800 height=652 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and engaging gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mahjong solitaire is the best way to relax. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/1302c80bbf919b82e1c57a0f88b19770.poster.avif?t=1730482880\" width=800 height=573 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/1302c80bbf919b82e1c57a0f88b19770.webm?t=1730482880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120 puzzle levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy and relaxed gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special tiles for new gameplay twists</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the mysterious world of Ancient Egypt! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find matching tiles, solve mahjong levels and collect artifacts to uncover secrets of Giza valley, Old city, Desert and Nile.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/f3c6ff7a5d81ba425bd1421bb71743bf.avif?t=1730482880\" width=642 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Restore artifacts collection!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover how the Great Pyramid of Giza was constructed, how Egyptians learned to read hieroglyphs, why Only the pharaoh could own a cat in Ancient Egypt and many more surprising facts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/14d17df1595897670fbc1e5b31474690.poster.avif?t=1730482880\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/14d17df1595897670fbc1e5b31474690.webm?t=1730482880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We made it even better with new game features. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you will find huge treasures, tricky locks, new bonus tiles and more. Solving some layouts is not easy, but you can always use powerups to beat the most challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/f40d1433067430f126b8a298988c5257.avif?t=1730482880\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras_big/f40d1433067430f126b8a298988c5257.avif?t=1730482880 width=800 height=652 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and engaging gameplay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mahjong solitaire is the best way to relax. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/1302c80bbf919b82e1c57a0f88b19770.poster.avif?t=1730482880\" width=800 height=573 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220080/extras/1302c80bbf919b82e1c57a0f88b19770.webm?t=1730482880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120 puzzle levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy and relaxed gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special tiles for new gameplay twists</p></li></ul>",
